  h3 Messages

  h4 Basic messages
  p 
    | There are four types of styles for messages: 
    code.inline-light default
    |  ,
    code.inline-light alert
    |  ,
    code.inline-light error
    |  and 
    code.inline-light success
    |  . 
    | All of them can contain links, which will have appropriate colors.

  .message
    p 
      | This is a message. 
      a(href="") This is a link.

  .message.message-error
    p 
      | This is an error. 
      a(href="") This is a link.

  .message.message-alert
    p
      | This is an alert. 
      a(href="") This is a link.

  .message.message-success
    p 
      | This is a success message. 
      a(href="") This is a link.

